divs: Sighting DetailsMy name is Jim Christie on March 19 2012 My girfriend and I went on a Carnival cruise to the Bahamas, on the last night out to sea when the sun was setting over the ocean I told my girlfriend to look at the sunset and I started taking pictures. I took a total of five photos and it was not until tonight that I looked at them on my cell phone while cleaning out old data. When I got to this picture I noticed the two lights and sent the photo to my computer to get a better look. I could not believe my eyes. Don't know what to do with this photo but I did not see anthing while taking the photo. Please advise Jim Christie
Summary: Took photos of sunset while out to sea and captured two UFO'S
